Test Cases
1. LOGIN PAGE TESTING
   -Test the admin login page with correct password and username.
   -Test the doctor login page with correct password and username.
   -Test the patient login page with incorrect password entered.
   -Test the patient login page with correct password and username.

2. REGISTER PAGE TESTING
   - Test the patient register page.

3. APPOINTMENT BOOKING TESTING
   - Test the correct flow of booking the appointment.
   - Test whether the appointment booking system can prevent double booking appointment
    of same date and time.

4. APPOINTMENT CANCELING TESTING
   - Test whether the upcoming appointment can be cancelled or not.

5. QUEUE STATUS DISPLAYING TESTING
   - Test the system whether can generate queue number autonmatically once
    the appointment is confirmed.
   - Test the system whether can predict the waiting time of each patient.
   - Test the system whether can display overview of real time queue status.

6. NOTIFICATION ALERT TESTING
   -Test the system whether can send SMS alert to the patient when the patient
    is in the next queue.
   -Test the system whether can send notification once the appointment is confirmed.
